# Verify the haxelib / lix run entry compiles via `--run` (same path as `haxelib run`).
# Avoid `--no-output -main`: tink_cli macros can error under that mode.
# hx3compat: travix.AuthCommand still references haxe.remoting.HttpConnection.
# Usage: haxe check-run.hxml
-cp src
-lib travix
-lib tink_cli
-lib hx3compat
-D no-deprecation-warnings
--run
why.benchkit.Run
help
